    "description": "<strong>这是终极僵尸增量游戏</strong><br>收集资源来扩展和升级你的基地。在末日世界中自动化防御和资源生产，打造一个自给自足的要塞。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/4bdef7da17bc007ef9d398a61222a674.poster.avif?t=1749838581\" width=600 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/4bdef7da17bc007ef9d398a61222a674.webm?t=1749838581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/4bdef7da17bc007ef9d398a61222a674.mp4?t=1749838581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>建立你的基地</strong><br>将你的营地改造成一个设有可升级结构的坚固堡垒，以抵御丧尸侵袭并满足生存需求。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/ae2ff86b00d440bc86d749d3940202fe.poster.avif?t=1749838581\" width=600 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/ae2ff86b00d440bc86d749d3940202fe.webm?t=1749838581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/ae2ff86b00d440bc86d749d3940202fe.mp4?t=1749838581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>在一个危险的世界中生存</strong><br>搜寻并探索充满有价值的武器、食物和补给的开放世界。面对丧尸横行的威胁，警惕可能潜伏在暗处的其他拾荒者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/a8f25945d4de61559ae78943ce9b1ba3.poster.avif?t=1749838581\" width=600 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/a8f25945d4de61559ae78943ce9b1ba3.webm?t=1749838581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/a8f25945d4de61559ae78943ce9b1ba3.mp4?t=1749838581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>自定义你的角色</strong><br>从数百个定制选项中选择，打造你理想的角色。",
